{
  "id": "RAW_5396f171",
  "title": "Gemini 3 Flash 现已在 Vercel AI 网关上线 – Vercel",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/changelog/gemini-3-flash-is-now-available-on-the-vercel-ai-gateway",
  "date": "2025-12-17 13:00:00",
  "author": "Walter Korman, Matt Lenhard, Jerilyn Zheng",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__9eLiuW__content\">\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">You can now access Google's latest Gemini model, Gemini 3 Flash, with Vercel's <a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI Gateway</a> and no other provider accounts required.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">It is Google's most intelligent model that is optimized for speed, with Gemini 3's pro-grade reasoning alongside flash-level latency, efficiency, and cost. Gemini 3 Flash significantly outperforms the previous Gemini 2.5 models, beating Gemini 2.5 Pro across most benchmarks, while using 30% less tokens and is 3x faster at a fraction of the cost.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">To use the Gemini 3 Flash with the <a href=\"https://ai-sdk.dev/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://ai-sdk.dev/\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI SDK</a>, set the model to <code>google/gemini-3-flash</code>:</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-tsx code-block-module__NOThwW__pre blog-code-block-module__zaYDqW__maxHeight\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> streamText </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'ai'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> result </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">streamText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'google/gemini-3-flash'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  prompt</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token template-string string\">Produce a step-by-step analysis that solves a novel</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token template-string string\">     problem, exposes intermediate logic, and delivers a final answer</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L8\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token template-string string\">     using minimal tokens and maximal inference density.</span><span class=\"token template-string template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L9\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  providerOptions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L10\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    google</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L11\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      thinkingLevel</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'high'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L12\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      includeThoughts</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L13\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L14\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C23d1170f-L15\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">AI Gateway provides a unified API for calling models, tracking usage and cost, and configuring retries, failover, and performance optimizations for higher-than-provider uptime. It includes built-in <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/observability\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/observability\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">observability</a>, <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/byok\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/byok\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Bring Your Own Key support</a>, and intelligent <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/provider-options\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/provider-options\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">provider routing</a> with automatic retries.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Learn more about <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI Gateway</a>, view the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway/leaderboards\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway/leaderboards\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI Gateway model leaderboard</a> or try it in our <a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway/models/gemini-3-flash\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway/models/gemini-3-flash\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">model playground</a>.</p>\n   <a href=\"https://vercel.com/ai-gateway/leaderboards\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link flex flex-col items-center justify-start flex-initial inline-cta-module__xGJe4a__wrapper\"> \n    <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-stretch justify-start gap-4 md:gap-6 flex-initial inline-cta-module__xGJe4a__content\">\n     <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-1 flex-initial\">\n      <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper inline-cta-module__xGJe4a__text\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:1rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400\"><span class=\"inline-cta-module__xGJe4a__icon\"> \n        <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n         <g clip-path=\"url(#clip0_872_3186)\">\n          <circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"8\" r=\"7.25\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></circle> <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8 4.5L11.5 10.625H4.5L8 4.5Z\" fill=\"var(--ds-gray-100)\"></path>\n         </g>\n         <defs>\n          <clipPath id=\"clip0_872_3186\">\n           <rect width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"white\"></rect>\n          </clipPath>\n         </defs>\n        </svg> \n       </span><strong>AI Gateway: Track top AI models by usage</strong></p>\n      <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:1rem;--text-line-height:1.5rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\">The AI Gateway model leaderboard ranks the most used models over time by total token volume across all traffic through the Gateway. Updates regularly.</p>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"flex flex-col items-start justify-center flex-initial\">\n      <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper inline-cta-module__xGJe4a__cta\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:500\">View the leaderboard</p>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p class=\"text-module__eElGjq__wrapper text-module__fl7lUq__paragraph\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel AI 网关现已支持谷歌最新的 Gemini 3 Flash 模型，该模型以优化的速度、效率和成本效益，赋能 AI 开发。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel AI 网关现已支持谷歌最新的 Gemini 3 Flash 模型，该模型以优化的速度、效率和成本效益，赋能 AI 开发。",
  "summary": "Vercel AI 网关宣布支持谷歌最新、最智能的 Gemini 3 Flash 模型。用户无需额外服务商账户，即可直接通过 Vercel 平台访问该模型。Gemini 3 Flash 在大多数基准测试中表现优于此前的 Gemini 2.5 Pro 模型，性能更佳，同时 Token 使用量降低 30%，速度提升三倍，而成本仅为其一小部分。文章提供了一个使用 AI SDK 调用 Gemini 3 Flash 的代码示例，展示了如何通过简单配置实现复杂的推理任务。Vercel AI 网关提供统一的 API，用于使用量跟踪、成本管理、重试、故障转移和性能优化，确保 AI 应用的高可用性。此外，它还包括内置的可观测性、自带密钥 (BYOK) 支持，以及带有自动重试功能的智能提供商路由，大大简化了 AI 模型集成和管理。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Vercel AI 网关无缝集成了 Gemini 3 Flash，简化了最新模型的使用。",
      "explanation": "开发者现在可以直接通过 Vercel AI 网关访问 Gemini 3 Flash，无需配置额外的服务商账户，从而降低了集成复杂性并加速了开发工作流程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gemini 3 Flash 在性能和成本效益方面取得了显著提升。",
      "explanation": "该模型在大多数基准测试中超越了 Gemini 2.5 Pro，Token 使用量减少 30%，运行速度提升三倍，并以更低的成本提供高性能的推理能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 网关提供全面的模型管理和优化功能。",
      "explanation": "Vercel AI 网关提供统一的 API，通过使用量跟踪、成本管理、自动重试、故障转移、可观测性和智能路由等功能，确保 AI 应用高效运行并具备高可用性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "您现在可以通过 Vercel 的 AI 网关访问谷歌最新的 Gemini 模型 Gemini 3 Flash，无需其他服务商账户。",
    "Gemini 3 Flash 在大多数基准测试中显著优于此前的 Gemini 2.5 Pro 模型，同时 Token 使用量减少 30%，速度提升三倍，而成本仅为其一小部分。",
    "AI 网关提供统一的 API，用于调用模型、跟踪使用量和成本，并配置重试、故障转移和性能优化，以提供比提供商更高的正常运行时间。"
  ],
